<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>🎮 Mini Game</title>
<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    font-family:Arial;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
}
.box{
    text-align:center;
}
button{
    padding:15px 30px;
    font-size:18px;
    cursor:pointer;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="box">
    <h1>🎮 Clique para começar o minigame</h1>
    <p>Prometo que não tem susto... 😅</p>

    <button onclick="tocar()">Começar</button>

    <audio id="brazino" src="brazino.mp3"></audio>
</div>

<script>
function tocar(){
    document.getElementById("brazino").play();
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
